title: Gross domestic product ( GDP ) growth rate in Oman 2024
yAxis: GDP growth compared to previous year
summary: The statistic depicts france 's real gross domestic product ( gdp ) growth rate from 2014 to 2018 , with projections up until 2024 . gdp refers to the total market value of all goods and services that are produced within a country per year . It is an important indicator of the economic strength of a country .
gold: The statistic shows the growth in real GDP in Oman from 2014 to 2024  . In 2018 , Oman 's real gross domestic product increased by around 1.76 percent compared to the previous year .
